Package nl.naturalis.geneious.name

Class QueryCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.geneious.name.QueryCache
  • class QueryCache
extends Object
    Provides various types of lookups on a collection of Geneious documents, presumably fetched-and-cached using a database query.
